# kart.logs on a missing kart returns code:3 kart_not_found. This exercises
# the same "absent from both devpod and garage" branch that kart_info and
# kart_delete rely on, but through kart.logs' own registration path so a
# typo in the wire method constant or RegisterKartLifecycle surfaces.

stdin logs.json
lakitu rpc
! stderr .
stdout '"error":'
! stdout 'method_not_found'
stdout '"code":3'
stdout '"type":"kart_not_found"'
stdout '"kart":"ghost"'

-- logs.json --
{"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"kart.logs","params":{"name":"ghost"},"id":1}
